{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2032, "height": 2835, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜文忠：洛阳耐火材料设计研究院高级工程师。", "block_bbox": [151, 243, 1171, 300], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "徐坡：", "block_bbox": [151, 314, 269, 366], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五世杜光荣：字明德，幼擅书法，河南大学毕业，任中华民国河南省秘书，和中共地下党员何运宏结为好友。开封解放后，何运宏介绍其入河南军政干校学习，后在第四野战军五十八军一七三师工作。\n", "block_bbox": [149, 386, 1699, 583], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十六世杜海廷：解放军空军地空导弹学院毕业。曾任空军地空导弹独立第十五营座标测定技师、宜阳县委纪检委干部、洛阳地委统战部办公室主任兼洛阳地委机关党总支副书记，洛阳市委统战部办公室主任、落实政策办公室主任、经济联络科科长，洛阳市工商业联合会副会长兼理事长，洛阳市工商联调研员等职。洛阳市政协第八、九、十届委员。\n", "block_bbox": [147, 603, 1699, 939], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世青锋：大专学历，中教一级教师，曾任盐镇一中校长。", "block_bbox": [151, 957, 1252, 1015], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世青林：中师毕业，小教高级教师。", "block_bbox": [153, 1029, 885, 1084], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜联成：曾任朝川矿务局一矿任团委书记、机关党支部书记等职，助理政工师职称。后任平煤集团朝川矿一井基层区队支部书记等职。2002年平顶山工业职业技术学院安全管理专业毕业（中专）。2005年于平煤党校经济管理专业毕业（大专），2008年获矿山开采技术员职称。\n", "block_bbox": [146, 1100, 1697, 1368], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜国伟：中国政法大学法学专业本科，在伊川县人民法院工作。", "block_bbox": [152, 1385, 1448, 1442], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜春晓：女，洛阳师专毕业。", "block_bbox": [151, 1458, 800, 1511], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜双喜：本科毕业，现任河南省人事厅干部科长。", "block_bbox": [150, 1529, 1190, 1585], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜克辉：研究生毕业，现在国家煤炭部工作。", "block_bbox": [148, 1600, 1106, 1659], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十九世杜占锋：郑州大学毕业。", "block_bbox": [148, 1672, 735, 1730], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "西窑：", "block_bbox": [148, 1747, 269, 1799], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜国锋：郑州财经学院专科。", "block_bbox": [148, 1819, 824, 1874], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜玲玲：大专。", "block_bbox": [148, 1893, 562, 1947], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十八世杜乃栋：北京中国政法大学毕业，任职于首都机场。", "block_bbox": [147, 1964, 1241, 2023], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "东张村：", "block_bbox": [149, 2041, 316, 2094], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十六世杜宗文：本科毕业，任三门峡市人大教科文卫副主任。热心族谊，书法极佳。", "block_bbox": [147, 2113, 1692, 2171], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜保现：本科。中学教师。", "block_bbox": [148, 2188, 787, 2244], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜鹏举：宗文长子，清华北大深造。", "block_bbox": [145, 2260, 938, 2316], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜阳勇：大专学历。", "block_bbox": [145, 2333, 652, 2388], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜阳杰：大专学历。", "block_bbox": [145, 2404, 652, 2460], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜阳华：大专学历。", "block_bbox": [146, 2476, 652, 2531], "block_id": 22, "block_order": 23}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十七世杜书军：广东军区上校团长。", "block_bbox": [145, 2548, 829, 2603], "block_id": 23, "block_order": 24}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1813, 742, 1894, 1472], "block_id": 24, "block_order": 25}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三三〇", "block_bbox": [1822, 2149, 1878, 2276], "block_id": 25, "block_order": 26}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.63984215259552, "coordinate": [149.25, 2041.541259765625, 316.94879150390625, 2094.142333984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6240689158439636, "coordinate": [146.79620361328125, 1100.962890625, 1697.7587890625, 1368.01953125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6058552861213684, "coordinate": [147.83099365234375, 603.2197875976562, 1699.923583984375, 939.9065551757812]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5881437063217163, "coordinate": [149.8720703125, 386.59600830078125, 1699.0806884765625, 583.2305297851562]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5285815596580505, "coordinate": [147.42938232421875, 1964.541748046875, 1241.148681640625, 2023.139892578125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5252197980880737, "coordinate": [152.4599609375, 1385.830322265625, 1448.862548828125, 1442.569091796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5231456756591797, "coordinate": [151.67120361328125, 1458.164306640625, 800.0365600585938, 1511.842529296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5134713649749756, "coordinate": [150.30938720703125, 1529.5419921875, 1190.650634765625, 1585.2236328125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5051335692405701, "coordinate": [151.80914306640625, 243.062255859375, 1171.904296875, 300.38409423828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5027620792388916, "coordinate": [148.01016235351562, 1600.7900390625, 1106.4088134765625, 1659.51416015625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.5008456707000732, "coordinate": [148.55767822265625, 1747.85