佳。\n\n十七世杜保现：本科。中学教师。\n\n十七世杜鹏举：宗文长子，清华北大深造。\n\n十七世杜阳勇：大专学历。\n\n十七世杜阳杰：大专学历。\n\n十七世杜阳华：大专学历。\n\n十七世杜书军：广东军区上校团长。\n\n## 渑池杜氏宗谱\n\n三三〇", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//67da00cc-97ff-4105-bd21-f2e06ef3ad30/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A22Z%2F-1%2F%2Ffdfd541f59545910d2481682ca18f7011442afc7e5fd4f41def54fc6768a7cc3", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//67da00cc-97ff-4105-bd21-f2e06ef3ad30/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A22Z%2F-1%2F%2F0a23554483e09023096dbee40e8dcc4dab63e229c10735272393809cf567eacf", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//67da00cc-97ff-4105-bd21-f2e06ef3ad30/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A23Z%2F-1%2F%2Fac1c324e47cda7cee430d37653c059ef0d33f5ad680337cc60aa55130aed7cdf", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//67da00cc-97ff-4105-bd21-f2e06ef3ad30/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A23Z%2F-1%2F%2Fa83b0b213a11dc59c61c27b50207e6e281191f3957ab2c589930f6d7844d3402"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//67da00cc-97ff-4105-bd21-f2e06ef3ad30/input_img_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A28%3A22Z%2F-1%2F%2Fb9d11e2cfaf0a23bac5e77b1662b8a1d062f827bba8efae35f610c3a769d303e"}], "dataInfo": {"width": 2032, "height": 2835, "type": "image"}, "ocrResults": [{"prunedResult": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[159, 